Subject: [PATCH 2/3] mesh hooks: fix triggers, add has_media(), demote debug
 logs

- Fix images_no_multimodal trigger: was always true when hooks enabled,
  now correctly checks task.tokens.has_media() && !has_mtmd
- Add server_tokens::has_media() public accessor
- Add mesh_n_turns to task_params, parsed from messages array size
- Demote Hook 1/2 response logging from INF to DBG
- All three hooks tested end-to-end with mock server
